                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13990</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt; A client gets evicted and reconnects, so there can be a window&lt;br/&gt;
 with 2 exports with flocks from the same client.&lt;br/&gt;
  In this case during deadlock search from the new export we can go&lt;br/&gt;
  to the old export and back to the new one.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
